descriptionNullable:
Discussion about this dataset is [here][1]

These TFRecords contain Kaggle's Melanoma Classification competition's 30k Train and 10k Test images plus 30k External images with Meta Data. They have the following features:

    feature = {
      'image': _bytes_feature,
      'image_name': _bytes_feature,
      'patient_id': _int64_feature,
      'sex': _int64_feature,
      'age_approx': _int64_feature,
      'anatom_site_general_challenge': _int64_feature,
      'source': _int64_feature,
      'target': _int64_feature
    }

The test TFRecords do not have `target` nor `source`

[1]: https://www.kaggle.com/c/siim-isic-melanoma-classification/discussion/156245
